You can add row names (rowname_col argument) and add
group names (groupname_col argument) into the table:


iris %>% 
  arrange(desc(Sepal.Length)) %>% # 6 types of iris with largest sepal length
  mutate(Rank = paste0("ID", 1:nrow(.))) %>% 
  head(20) %>% 
  gt(groupname_col = "Species", 
     rowname_col = "Rank")



